Package camzup.core

Interface IBlenderWritable

All Known Implementing Classes:
ImageEntity2, ImageEntity3, MeshEntity2, MeshEntity3, TextEntity2, TextEntity3
public interface IBlenderWritable
A package-level interface to generate Blender boiler plate for various entities.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    default java.lang.StringBuilder genMaterialString​(java.lang.StringBuilder pyCd)
    Generates Blender python code which sets materials.

    Generates Blender python code which creates mesh data.
    default java.lang.StringBuilder genParentString​(java.lang.StringBuilder pyCd)
    Generates Blender python code which creates an empty parent object.
